    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004810/extras/7138318d52cc9deddb510d717d5b2dfa.poster.avif?t=1771771021\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004810/extras/7138318d52cc9deddb510d717d5b2dfa.webm?t=1771771021\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004810/extras/7138318d52cc9deddb510d717d5b2dfa.mp4?t=1771771021\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《诏者:轮卡》是一款具电影感的 Roguelike 牌组构筑游戏。你将扮演由<strong>机械诏命</strong>拣选的<strong>诏者</strong>，执行清剿与镇压任务。以机械卡牌发动攻击、进行格挡，在激烈的近战交锋中猎杀反抗者，并逐步揭开这个被机器意志操控的世界所隐藏的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004810/extras/361d58961f853959d6d0efcd29bdc65f.avif?t=1771771021\" width=616 height=347 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每张卡牌都可通过安装独特的「<strong>机壳</strong>」与「<strong>卡轮</strong>」组件来升级。每个组件都有其专属外观与效果，善用它们优化你的卡牌，尝试不同的玩法与策略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004810/extras/c3811c02cd32138f66629cec067ab2d9.avif?t=1771771021\" width=616 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>可破坏卡牌</strong>：在战斗中被摧毁的卡牌，直到下一场战斗才会恢复。它们拥有独立的生命系统，以轮环上的数字与轮环类型来标示；其中轮环类型会影响伤害的计算方式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004810/extras/f8b5f63633deddaafb509f80130068b0.avif?t=1771771021\" width=616 height=201 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004810/extras/9ce59edf9e8b875dd23452f376cc8bbc.poster.avif?t=1771771021\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004810/extras/9ce59edf9e8b875dd23452f376cc8bbc.webm?t=1771771021\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004810/extras/9ce59edf9e8b875dd23452f376cc8bbc.mp4?t=1771771021\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>强力资源</strong>：可进一步强化你的组件-卡牌连携，或解锁全新的玩法策略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004810/extras/03c9b3c78db814ae82358d3df894ff33.poster.avif?t=1771771021\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004810/extras/03c9b3c78db814ae82358d3df894ff33.webm?t=1771771021\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004810/extras/03c9b3c78db814ae82358d3df894ff33.mp4?t=1771771021\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>激烈战斗</strong>：独特的战斗机制，会改变你的出牌节奏与策略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004810/extras/843e7d2c6eba7ed5dc0265f358e886fd.poster.avif?t=1771771021\" width=600 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004810/extras/843e7d2c6eba7ed5dc0265f358e886fd.webm?t=1771771021\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004810/extras/843e7d2c6eba7ed5dc0265f358e886fd.mp4?t=1771771021\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004810/extras/84e0b935d40ffca5043532a20e8ebc7e.poster.avif?t=1771771021\" width=600 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004810/extras/84e0b935d40ffca5043532a20e8ebc7e.webm?t=1771771021\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004810/extras/84e0b935d40ffca5043532a20e8ebc7e.mp4?t=1771771021\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>连锁机制</strong>：探索多种串联方式，把思路接成强力连招。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004810/extras/b405a397512beeaeaa6e86c030503426.avif?t=1771771021\" width=616 height=347 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >性能优化到位：在多数设备上都能稳定流畅运行；并以 <strong>Steam Deck Verified</strong> 为目标推进适配，力求首发支持。</p>",
